            "title": "首掛3新股全高收 兆易創新表現最佳升逾37% 每手賬賺6080元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今日登場3隻新股全部成功守住招股價收市，當中以兆易創新(03986)表現最佳，收報222.8元，較招股價162元高37.53%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：兆易創新官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251218_FI_source-web_Giga-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：兆易創新官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251218_FI_source-web_Giga-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：兆易創新官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以該股1手100股計，認購並獲配每手賬面賺6080元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一隻於主板掛牌的新股紅星冷鏈(01641)則高開低走，最高曾見19.7元，較招股偎12.26元高60.69%，但升幅迅速收窄，最低曾見12元，較招股價低2.12%；收報12.3元，略高於招股價0.33%。以該股1手500股計，認購並獲配每手賬面賺20元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：紅星冷鏈官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251229_FI_source-web_HNHXLL.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：紅星冷鏈官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251229_FI_source-web_HNHXLL.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：紅星冷鏈官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於在GEM上市的BBSB(08610)，今早高開4倍後一度衝上3.11元，較招股價0.6元高4.18倍，但同樣高開低走兼一度「潛水」，最低見0.59元，低於招股價1.67%；收報0.67元，較招股價高11.67%。以該股1手4000股計，認購並獲配每手賬面賺320元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15578974-%e9%a6%96%e6%8e%9b3%e6%96%b0%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a8%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6-%e5%85%86%e6%98%93%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e8%a1%a8%e7%8f%be%e6%9c%80%e4%bd%b3%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be37-%e6%af%8f%e6%89%8b%e8%b3%ac%e8%b3%ba6080",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03986.jpg.webp",
